lincoln davenport chafee ( ; born march 26 , 1953 ) is an american politician from rhode island who has served as the mayor of warwick , rhode island , in the united states senate , and as the 74th governor of rhode island .

before i was elected : senator lincoln chafee of this new england state spent 7 years as a blacksmith at racetracks in the u.s. & canada

